title: Abstraction Point January-June 2008 Collection
description:
The Abstraction Point has survived another six months, and we&#039;ve been busy making new tunes for you all to enjoy.

The tracks posted here are all the tracks collected in our Beat Exchange board between January and June this year.

All tracks, except for the Calabria rearrangements, and SubArtic&#039;s material, are licensed under the Creative Commons BY-NC-SA 3.0 license.

Please enjoy this newest collection of music, and feel free to share! We appreciate your support!

If you want to help us out, or even contribute your own stuff, you can find us at http://www.abstractionpoint.net.

Sign up on the forums and make yourself at home!

-- PEACE --
From the AP Crew
